---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="关于" description="关于建筑师与设计工作室">
  <header class="page-header">
    <p class="page-eyebrow">Studio</p>
    <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
  </header>

  <section class="about-body">
    <div class="about-col about-col--main">
      <p>
        Open & Link 开合建筑，是位于深圳的小型建筑工作室。事务所专注动态可变设计，
        挖掘空间随时间、行为、环境变化的可能性。
        团队核心聚焦于：光伏低碳能源整合、装配式建造体系、建筑生产工艺优化；
        并长期深耕木结构与轻型建筑研究，擅长低自重、低碳排、快速落地的轻量化建造实践。
        项目覆盖装置、文旅木构、产业厂房、小型公建、城市微更新等多元尺度，坚持从构造源头推导设计，打通方案、预制加工与现场装配，以小团队精细化实现兼具灵活性、可持续性与落地性的建筑作品。
      </p>
      <p>
         Open & Link Architects is a boutique Shenzhen-based studio focusing on kinetic,
         transformable design that responds to time, human use and surroundings.
         Our core research covers integrated PV low-carbon systems, prefabricated construction and fabrication techniques. We have extensive experience in mass timber and lightweight structures, delivering low-carbon, quick-to-build lightweight projects.
         Our cross-scale works range from installations, 
         timber tourism buildings and industrial premises to small public architecture and urban micro-renewal. Guided by tectonic logic, we connect conceptual design, off-site prefabrication and on-site assembly. Our lean team creates refined architecture balancing flexibility, sustainability and constructability.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-col about-col--side">
      <dl class="about-meta">
        <div class="am-item">
          <dt>Location</dt>
          <dd>中国 · 深圳</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="am-item">
          <dt>Contact</dt>
          <dd><a href="mailto:studio@openlink.arch">studio@openlink.arch</a></dd>
        </div>
        <div class="am-item">
          <dt>Practice</dt>
          <dd>建筑设计 / Architecture</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 4rem 0 2.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-rule);
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }
  .page-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--ff-caps);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-mid);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--ff-caps);
    font-size: 28pt;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-col--main p {
    font-family: var(--ff-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    line-height: var(--lh-body);
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    text-align: justify;
    hyphens: auto;
  }

  .about-meta {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--c-rule);
  }
  .am-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-rule);
  }
  .am-item dt {
    font-family: var(--ff-caps);
    font-size: 6.5pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-mid);
  }
  .am-item dd {
    font-family: var(--ff-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    color: var(--c-ink);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .about-body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>